body_html:
@pisiiki They are not the same data type, v and foo are not the same type either. The above code has the same issue on Linux and returns inf too.
The tf.control_dependencies is nothing but a wrapper for Graph.control_dependencies() using the default graph. You can also convert from one data type to the other.
